some experimentation at creating Knife Plug-ins

[+] ./chef_plugins_knife/task_role_rename.rb  
 |+ added a Chef Role Rename task
 |+syntax: 'knife lab role rename CURRENT_ROLE_NAME NEW_ROLE_NAME'

[+] ./chef_plugins_knife/myversions.rb
 |+ plain trial plug-in listing chef gem versions 
 |+syntax: 'knife lab chef versions'

[][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][]
**  USAGE **

[+] Copy required Plug-in Ruby Scripts from 
    this repo's 'chef_plugins_knife' directory to
    chef repo's './.chef/plugins/knife/' directory
 and then do 
    $ knife --help
      it's commands will get listed as 
      'knife lab .....'
[][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][][]


